	* libltdl/m4/libtool.m4 (_LT_COMPILER_PIC, _LT_LANG_CXX_CONFIG)
	(_LT_SYS_HIDDEN_LIBDEPS) [solaris]: Accept compiler names sunCC,
	sunf77, sunf90, sunf95 in addition to CC, f77, f90, f95.
	* NEWS: Update.
